"<html><head/><body><p>Setting the camera position angle shall move the "
"rotator. The gauge reflects the state of the rotator. Depending on the "
"accuracy of the rotator there can be some deviation in the ending position "
"angle.</p><p>The position angle is measured East of North in degrees.</p></"
"body></html>"
msgstr ""

