#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, focusRefineCurveFit)
#. +> trunk5
#: ekos/focus/opsfocusprocess.ui:403
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Check to run an outlier pass when all datapoints have "
"been taken. The pass uses Peirce's Criteria for outlier threshold detection. "
"If there are outliers, these are removed and curve fitting rerun. If the R² "
"is improved by the process then this new dataset is used and outliers "
"highlighted on the v-curve. </p></body></html>"
msgstr ""

