"pulses are sent, but the resultant pixel dithering amount is not enforced so "
"only the one dither pulse is sent. This is quicker, and recommended as "
"dither amount is random anyway. It is necessary when 2-D dither is required "
"but guiding is only done in one axis.</p></body></html>"
