#. +> trunk5
#: kstars.kcfg:387
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If true, trails attached to solar system bodies will fade into the "
"background sky color."
msgstr "有効にすると、太陽系の惑星の光跡が背景色に溶け込みます。"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (FocusRA), group (View)
#. +> trunk5
#: kstars.kcfg:391
#, kde-format
