"Enter the Country name for the desired location.  It might be easier to use "
"the \"Find City...\" button to choose your location from the list of "
"predefined cities."
msgstr ""
"目的の場所の国名を入力します。「都市を検索」を使ってあらかじめ定義されたリス"
